content: suleigolden: Merged two significant PRs this month: a new football plugin feature (#2461) with substantial code changes (+281,878/-73,240 lines) and a type error fix for the animated.div component (#2462) with +62,206/-7,064 lines. Provided 7 review comments on other PRs, showing engagement with the team's work. Activity was sporadic, contributing on just 4 days this month, with a primary focus on feature development (67%) and bug fixes (22%).
